file.name: record.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Main Openapi Yaml
  version: 0.1.0
servers:
  - url: "{server}:{port}"
    variables:
      server:
        default: http://localhost
      port:
        default: "9090"
paths:
  /:
    get:
      operationId: operation_get
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Ok
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pet'

components:
  schemas:
    Pet:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
        address:
          type: array
          items:
            type: array
            items:
              type: string
        type:
          type: string
